    {
      "Text": "Security update for util-linux",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for util-linux fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2025-14104: Fixed heap buffer overread in setpwnam() when processing 256-byte usernames (bsc#1254666).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
